     C                     Z-ADD1         RCDNBR
      *
     C                     Z-ADDRRN       XXRRN   50
B001 C                     DO   *HIVAL    RRN@@   50
     C           RRN@@     CHAINDSP2R                42
B002 C           *IN,42    IFEQ '0'
B003 C           OP        IFEQ 'M'
      *  ﾅﾎﾞﾎｦbﾓ ﾍﾍｭcﾆﾞ ---> fﾞx]2 ﾉ ﾎｧｰﾓnﾞ
     C                     MOVEL#KNKB     XXKNKB
